tart to end- Worked extensively with databases like MySQL, Oracle and sybase.- Worked as  Unix System Admin for Solaris 8, Linux RHE, CentOS, and Ubuntu.The current project is being developed by a team of 3 and my role is implementing Ajax code,SOAP/php, WS , MySQL and CSS. Prior to this project I have developed several web based applications for Stanford Law school for Alumni connection. I am very disciplined and can work independently with minimal supervision.Please find a copy of my resume attached to the email Thank you very much. -Kitara510-995-7552','2009-10-20 19:14:16','');
