a> to play the clip in your browser.</audio></div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"padding:0.6em 0 0.3em;text-align:center;\">\n<div class=\"center\">\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Location_Tunisia_AU_Africa.svg\" class=\"image\" title=\"Location of &#160;Tunisia&#160;&#160;(dark blue)–&#160;in Africa&#160;&#160;(light blue &amp;&#160;dark grey)–&#160;in the African Union&#160;&#160;(light blue)\"><img alt=\"Location of &#160;Tunisia&#160;&#160;(dark blue)–&#160;in Africa&#160;&#160;(light blue &amp;&#160;dark grey)–&#160;in the African Union&#160;&#160;(light blue)\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7c/Location_Tunisia_AU_Africa.svg/250px-Location_Tunisia_AU_Africa.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"232\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7c/Location_Tunisia_AU_Africa.svg/375px-Location_Tunisia_AU_Africa.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7c/Location_Tunisia_AU_Africa.svg/500px-Location_Tunisia_AU_Africa.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"1400\" data-file-height=\"1300\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"padding:0.3em;line-height:1.2em;font-size:85%;\">\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:11px;line-height:1.15em;\"><span style=\"font-size:11px;\">Location of <span style=\"font-size:2px;\">&#160;</span><strong class=\"selflink\">Tunisia</strong><span style=\"font-size:8px;\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">&#160;&#160;</span></span>(<span style=\"font-size:9px;\">dark blue</span>)</span>\n<p style=\"width:250px;font-size:11px;text-align:left;margin-left:1.2ex;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:1.15em;\">–&#160;in <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Africa\" title=\"Africa\">Africa</a><span style=\"font-size:8px;\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">&#160;&#160;</span></span>(<span style=\"font-size:9px;\">light blue &amp;&#160;dark grey</span>)<br />\n–&#160;in the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/African_U