=\"reference\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Egypt#cite_note-1\"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-USDept_of_State.2FEgypt_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Egypt#cite_note-USDept_of_State.2FEgypt-2\"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></span><sup class=\"reference\" id=\"ref_offlang\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Egypt#endnote_offlang\">[c]</a></sup></td>\n<td><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Circa\" title=\"Circa\">c.</a> 3150 BC&#160;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"mergedrow\">\n<td style=\"width:1.0em;padding:0 0 0 0.6em;\">&#160;-&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"padding-left:0;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Muhammad_Ali_Dynasty\" title=\"Muhammad Ali Dynasty\" class=\"mw-redirect\">Muhammad Ali Dynasty</a> inaugurated</td>\n<td>9 July 1805<sup id=\"cite_ref-Crabit.C3.A8s_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Egypt#cite_note-Crabit.C3.A8s-3\"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup>&#160;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"mergedrow\">\n<td style=\"width:1.0em;padding:0 0 0 0.6em;\">&#160;-&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"padding-left:0;\"><span class=\"nowrap\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unilateral_Declaration_of_Egyptian_Independence\" title=\"Unilateral Declaration of Egyptian Independence\">Independence</a> from<br />\nthe <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_Kingdom_of_Great_Britain_and_Ireland\" title=\"United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland\">United Kingdom</a></span></td>\n<td>28 February 1922&#160;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"mergedrow\">\n<td style=\"width:1.0em;padding:0 0 0 0.6em;\">&#160;-&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"padding-left:0;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Egyptian_Revolution_of_1952\" title=\"Egyptian Revolution of 1952\">Republic declared</a></td>\n<td>18 June 1953&#160;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"mergedrow\">\n<td style=\"width:1.0em;padding:0 0 0 0.6em;\">&#160;-&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"padding-left:0;\"><a href=\"http://en.