60;groups</a></b> (2014)</td>\n<td>Ethnic groups:\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Owambo_people\" title=\"Owambo people\" class=\"mw-redirect\">Ovambo</a>&#160;: 49.5%</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kavango_people\" title=\"Kavango people\">Kavango</a>: 9.2%</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coloured\" title=\"Coloured\">coloured</a> (including <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Baster\" title=\"Baster\">basters</a>): 8%</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Herero_people\" title=\"Herero people\">Herero</a>: 7%</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Damara_(people)\" title=\"Damara (people)\" class=\"mw-redirect\">Damara</a>: 7%</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/White_Namibians\" title=\"White Namibians\">Namibian whites</a>: 7.0%</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nama_people\" title=\"Nama people\">Nama</a>: 4.7%</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lozi_people\" title=\"Lozi people\">lozi</a> (Caprivian): 3.5%</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/San_people\" title=\"San people\">Bushmen</a>&#160;:3%</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tswana_people\" title=\"Tswana people\">Tswana</a>: 0.6%</li>\n<li>others: 0.5%</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Demonym\" title=\"Demonym\">Demonym</a></th>\n<td>Namibian</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Politics_of_Namibia\" title=\"Politics of Namibia\">Government</a></th>\n<td><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unitary_state\" title=\"Unitary state\">Unitary</a> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Presidential_system\" title=\"Presidential system\">presidential</a> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Constitutional_republic\" title=\"Constitutional republic\" class=\"mw-redirect\">constitutional republic</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"mergedrow\">\n<td style=\"width: