http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Telephone_numbers_in_Seychelles\" title=\"Telephone numbers in Seychelles\">Calling code</a></th>\n<td><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%2B248\" title=\"+248\" class=\"mw-redirect\">+248</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"mergedtoprow\">\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166\" title=\"ISO 3166\">ISO 3166 code</a></th>\n<td><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166-2:SC\" title=\"ISO 3166-2:SC\">SC</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Country_code_top-level_domain\" title=\"Country code top-level domain\">Internet TLD</a></th>\n<td><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/.sc\" title=\".sc\">.sc</a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p><b>Seychelles</b> (<span class=\"nowrap\"><span class=\"noexcerpt\"><a href=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4f/En-us-Seychelles.ogg\" title=\"Listen\"><img alt=\"Listen\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3b/Speakerlink-new.svg/11px-Speakerlink-new.svg.png\" width=\"11\" height=\"11\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3b/Speakerlink-new.svg/17px-Speakerlink-new.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3b/Speakerlink-new.svg/22px-Speakerlink-new.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"11\" data-file-height=\"11\" /></a><sup><span style=\"color: #00e; font: bold 80% sans-serif; padding: 0 .1em;\" class=\"IPA\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:En-us-Seychelles.ogg\" title=\"File:En-us-Seychelles.ogg\">i</a></span></sup></span><span title=\"Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)\" class=\"IPA\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA_for_English\" title=\"Help:IPA for English\">/</a></span><span class=\"IPA nopopups\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA_for_English#Key\" title=\"Help:IPA for English\"><span title=\"\'s\' in \'sigh\'\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dotted\">s</span></a></span><span class=\"IPA nopopups\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA_for_English#Key\" title=\"Help:IPA for English\"><span title=\"/eɪ/ long \'a\' in \'base\'\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dotted\">eɪ</span></a></span><span class=\"IPA nopopups\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA_for_English#Key\" title=\"Help:IPA for English\"><span title=\"/ˈ/ primary stress follows\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dotted\">ˈ</span></a></span><span class=\"IPA nopopups\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA_for_English#Key\" title=\"Help:IPA for English\"><span title=\"/ʃ/ \'sh\' in \'shy\'\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dotted\">ʃ</span></a></span><span class=\"IPA nopopups\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA_for_English#Key\" title=\"Help:IPA for English\"><span title=\"/ɛ/ short \'e\' in \'bed\'\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dotted\">ɛ</span></a></span><span class=\"IPA nopopups\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA_for_English#Key\" title=\"Help:IPA for English\"><span title=\"\'l\' in \'lie\'\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dotted\">l</span></a></span><span class=\"IPA nopopups\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA_for_English#Key\" title=\"Help:IPA for English\"><span title=\"\'z\' in \'zebra\'\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dotted\">z</span></a></span><span title=\"Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)\" class=\"IPA\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA_for_English\" title=\"Help:IPA for English\">/</a></span></span> <span title=\"English pronunciation respelling\" class=\"Unicode\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Pronunciation_respelling_key\" title=\"Wikipedia:Pronunciation respelling key\"><i>say-<b><span class=\"smallcaps\"><span class=\"SMALLCAPS\" style=\"FONT-VARIANT:SMALL-CAPS;\"><span class=\"NOCAPS\" style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM:LOWERCASE;\">SHELZ</span></span></span></b></i></a></span>; French: <span title=\"Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)\" class=\"IPA\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA_for_French\" title=\"Help:IPA for French\">[sɛʃɛl]</a></span>), officially the <b>Republic of Seychelles</b> (<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/French_language\" title=\"French language\">French</a>: <span lang=\"fr\"><i>République des Seychelles</i></span>; <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seychellois_Creole\" title=\"Seychellois Creole\">Creole</a>: <i>Repiblik Sesel</i>), is an <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Archipelago\" title=\"Archipelago\">archipelago</a> in the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indian_Ocean\" title=\"Indian Ocean\">Indian Ocean</a>. The 115-<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Island_country\" title=\"Island country\">island country</a>, whose capital is <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victoria,_Seychelles\" title=\"Victoria, Seychelles\">Victoria</a>, lies 1,500 kilometres (932&#160;mi) east of mainland <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Southeast_Africa\" title=\"Southeast Africa\" class=\"mw-redirect\">Southeast Africa</a>. Other nearby island countries and territories include <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zanzibar\" title=\"Zanzibar\">Zanzibar</a> to the west and <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comoros\" title=\"Comoros\">Comoros</a>, <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mayotte\" title=\"Mayotte\">Mayotte</a>, <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madagascar\" title=\"Madagascar\">Madagascar</a>, <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/R%C3%A9union\" title=\"Réunion\">Réunion</a> and <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mauritius\" title=\"Mauritius\">Mauritius</a> to the south.</p>\n<p>Seychelles, with a population of 90,024, has the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_African_countries_by_population\" title=\"List of African countries by population\">smallest population of any African state</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seychelles#cite_note-4\"><span>[</span>4<span>]</span></a></sup> Seychelles is a member of the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/African_Union\" title=\"African Union\">African Union</a>.</p>\n<p></p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\">\n<div id=\"toctitle\"'),(131,NULL,'Liberia',NULL,'upload/Liberia.txt',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-10-22 08:27:30','	<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\">Liberia</h1>\n		<div id=\"bodyContent\">\n			<h3 id=\"siteSub\"></h3>\n			<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n									<div id=\"jump-to-nav\">Jump to: <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberia#column-one\">navigation</a>, <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberia#searchInput\">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->\n			<div class=\"dablink\">This article is about the country in Africa.  For the city, see <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberia,_Costa_Rica\" title=\"Liberia, Costa Rica\">Liberia, Costa Rica</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox geography vcard\" style=\"width: 22em; font-size: 88%\">\n<tr class=\"adr\">\n<th colspan=\"3\" align=\"center\" class=\"mergedtoprow fn org country-name\" style=\"line-height:1.2em; padding:0.25em 0.33em 0.33em; font-size:1.25em;\">Republic of Liberia</th>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"mergedtoprow\">\n<td class=\"maptable\" colspan=\"3\" align=\"center\" style=\"padding:0.5em 0;\">\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; background:none;\">\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"width:58%; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Flag_of_Liberia.svg\" class=\"image\" title=\"Flag of Liberia\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b8/Flag_of_Liberia.svg/125px-Flag_of_Liberia.svg.png\" width=\"125\" height=\"66\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"width:auto; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Coat_of_arms_of_Liberia.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Coat of arms of Liberia\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/