ass=\"reference\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sierra_Leone#cite_note-imf2-3\"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"mergedtoprow\">\n<td colspan=\"2\"><b><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gross_domestic_product\" title=\"Gross domestic product\">GDP</a></b>&#160;(nominal)</td>\n<td>2012&#160;estimate</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"mergedrow\">\n<td style=\"width:1.0em;padding:0 0 0 0.6em;\">&#160;-&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"padding-left:0;\">Total</td>\n<td>$3.777&#160;billion<sup id=\"cite_ref-imf2_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sierra_Leone#cite_note-imf2-3\"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"mergedbottomrow\">\n<td style=\"width:1.0em;padding:0 0 0 0.6em;\">&#160;-&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"padding-left:0;\">Per capita</td>\n<td>$613<sup id=\"cite_ref-imf2_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sierra_Leone#cite_note-imf2-3\"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\"><b><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gini_coefficient\" title=\"Gini coefficient\">Gini</a></b>&#160;(2011)</td>\n<td>35.4<sup id=\"cite_ref-wb-gini_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sierra_Leone#cite_note-wb-gini-4\"><span>[</span>4<span>]</span></a></sup><br />\n<span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"><span style=\"color:orange\">medium</span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\"><b><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Human_Development_Index\" title=\"Human Development Index\">HDI</a></b> (2013)</td>\n<td><span title=\"Increase\"><img alt=\"Increase\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b0/Increase2.svg/11px-Increase2.svg.png\" width=\"11\" height=\"11\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b0/Increase2.svg/17px-Increase2.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b0/Increase2.svg/22px-Increase2.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"300\" data-file-height=\"300\" /></span>&#160;0.374<sup id=\"cite_ref-HDI_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sierra_Leone#cite_note-HDI-5\"><span>[</span>5<span>]</span></a></sup><br />\n<span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"><span style=\"color:red\">low</span></span>&#160;<b>·</b> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_Human_Development_Index\" title=\"List of countries by Human Development Index\">183rd</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">Currency</th>\n<td><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sierra_Leonean_leone\" title=\"Sierra Leonean leone\">Leone</a> (<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\" title=\"ISO 4217\">SLL</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Time zone</th>\n<td><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greenwich_Mean_Time\" title=\"Greenwich Mean Time\">GMT</a> <span class=\"nowrap\">(<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coordinated_Universal_Time\" title=\"Coordinated Universal Time\">UTC</a>+0)</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Drives on the</th>\n<td>right<sup>b</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Telephone_numbers_in_Sierra_Leone\" title=\"Telephone numbers in Sierra Leone\">Calling code</a></th>\n<td><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%2B232\" title=\"+232\" class=\"mw-redirect\">+232</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"mergedtoprow\">\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166\" title=\"ISO 3166\">ISO 3166 code</a></th>\n<td><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166-2:SL\" title=\"ISO 3166-2:SL\">SL</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Country_code_top-level_domain\" title=\"Country code top-level domain\">Internet TLD</a></th>\n<td><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/.sl\" title=\".sl\">.sl</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"font-size:85%;\">\n<td align=\"right\"><span style=\"position: relative; top: 0.3em;