ign:left;margin:0px 1px;border:none;text-weight:bold;display:none;\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fourth_dynasty_of_Egypt\" title=\"Fourth dynasty of Egypt\">4th Dynasty</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fifth_dynasty_of_Egypt\" title=\"Fifth dynasty of Egypt\">5th Dynasty</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sixth_dynasty_of_Egypt\" title=\"Sixth dynasty of Egypt\">6th Dynasty</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"NavFrame\">\n<div class=\"NavHead\" style=\"background-color:white;border:0px solid #000000;padding: 0px 0px 0px 4px; font-size: 100%; text-align:left;margin:0px;color:#330000\"><b><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/First_Intermediate_Period_of_Egypt\" title=\"First Intermediate Period of Egypt\"><font color=\"black\">First Intermediate</font></a></b></div>\n<div class=\"NavContent\" style=\"text-align:left;margin:0px 1px;border:none;text-weight:bold;display:none;\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seventh_dynasty_of_Egypt\" title=\"Seventh dynasty of Egypt\" class=\"mw-redirect\">7th Dynasty</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eighth_dynasty_of_Egypt\" title=\"Eighth dynasty of Egypt\" class=\"mw-redirect\">8th Dynasty</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ninth_dynasty_of_Egypt\" title=\"Ninth dynasty of Egypt\">9th Dynasty</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tenth_dynasty_of_Egypt\" title=\"Tenth dynasty of Egypt\">10th Dynasty</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eleventh_dynasty_of_Egypt\" title=\"Eleventh dynasty of Egypt\">11th Dynasty</a> (<i><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thebes,_Egypt\" title=\"Thebes, Egypt\">Thebes</a> only</i>)</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"NavFrame\">\n<div class=\"NavHead\" style=\"background-color:white;border:0px solid #000000;padding: 0px 0px 0px 4px; font-size: 100%; text-align:left;margin:0px;color:#330000\"><b><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/